author: Aksh
text:
She was a lioness in a birdcage, 
A bird in the depths of the sea. 
She was powerful and free 
but she was not where she should be...

author: Aksh
text:
The greatest gift you can give someone is the space to be his or herself, 
without the threat of you leaving....

author: Aksh
text:
If ur happiness is dependent on something outside u, den u are likely to become unhappy bcoz of it.
But if ur happiness is based on something dat is internal,
feelings of gratitude,contentment N the satisfaction frm having done one’s duty well,
Then dat happiness lives on.

author: Aksh
text:
Some flowers bloom in the day.
Some flowers bloom at night.
Some in spring, some in winter.
You are a flower. 
let you be You....

text:

 don't treat them ordinary...

author: Aksh
text:
You know yourself better than anyone else, 
yet you crumble at the words of someone 
who hasn't even lived a second of your life.

Focus on your own voice, 
It's the only one that matters...

author: Aksh
text:
Strong relationships are based on trust and communication.

But if there is no communication, there can be no trust...
